Comment_contributor: The Verbal Particle vu is prefixed to the true Numerals, as shown in twenty and thirteen.
[<vuru>, with both <u>s in italics, = “[difference from <u> is] shortness and sharpness”]
[<vu’ul>, with both <u>s in italics, = “[difference from <u> is] shortness and sharpness”]
[<sanwul>, with <n> in italics; <m> in italics, = “nasal”; <vuul>, with both <u>s in italics, = “[difference from <u> is] shortness and sharpness”]
